  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 125–Tea for Two.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第125课——两个人一起喝茶。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Does Susan have tea by herself?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "苏珊是独自喝茶吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Can't you come in and have tea now, Peter?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "彼得，你现在不能进来喝茶吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "还不行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I must water the garden first.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我得先给花园浇水。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Do you have to water it now?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你非得现在浇吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "I'm afraid I must.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "恐怕是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Look at it.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你看看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "It's terribly dry.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "干得厉害。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "What a nuisance!",
      "translation": {
        "text": "真讨厌！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Last summer it was very dry, too.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "去年夏天也很干。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Don't you remember?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你不记得了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "I had to water it every day.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我那时每天都得浇水。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Well, I'll have tea by myself.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那好吧，我自己喝茶。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "That was quick.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这么快就好了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Have you finished already?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你已经浇完了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是啊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Look out of the window.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "看看窗外。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "It's raining.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "下雨了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "That means you don't need to water the garden.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这就意味着你不用给花园浇水了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "That was a surprise.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "真没想到。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "It means I can have tea instead.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这意味着我可以改喝茶了。"
      }
    }
  ],
